Based on Jennifer Correa's profile, she has a Bachelor of Arts (BA) in Psychology and is currently working on her master's degree in Social Work. She has experience working in the non-profit organization's management industry, mental health, and with at-risk youth.

However, Jennifer does not have the qualifications for an LCSW (Licensed Clinical Social Worker) or psychiatry work, as she has not completed a Master's in Social Work and the necessary licensure and supervision requirements for LCSW. Additionally, psychiatry requires a medical degree (M.D. or D.O.), which Jennifer does not possess.

That being said, Jennifer's experience in mental health and social work may qualify her for positions related to case management, program coordination, or other roles within the mental health and social services fields.
